  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study was to examine the dose linearity of Roxane Laboratories' 15 mg,
      30 mg, and 60 mg codeine sulfate tablets under fasted conditions
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
